quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  39,8,"Si loraa memii neЙ—Й—o on, o noddira Joomi makko, ruttagol e Makko. Refti si O okkii mo moЖҙЖҙere, immorde ka Makko, o yejjita ko o noddaynoo kon ado Й—um, o waЙ—ana Allah kafidiiЙ—i, fii no o majjinira (yimЙ“e Й“en) e laawol Makko ngol. MaAku: \"Dakmitor keeferaaku maa ngun, seeЙ—a. Pellet, ko a jeyaaЙ—o e yimЙ“e Yiite Й“en"
  39,9,"Kaa ko on yankinotooЙ—o tummbo jemma, ko o sujjoowo, darotooЙ—o (naafe), hara himo laakara, himo jortii yurmeende Joomi makko nden... Maaku: \"Hara annduЙ“e Й“en fotay e Й“e anndaa Й“en?\" Anndu ko waajitotoo, ko joomiraaЙ“e haqqille Й“en"
  39,10,"Maaku: \"Ko onon yo jeyaaЙ“e Am gomЙ—imЙ“e, hulee Joomi mon\". Hino woodani moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e (golle) Й“en e oo aduna, mbarjaari. Leydi Allah ndin ko yaajundi. Anndee muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en timminirante njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndin, ko aldaa e limoore"
  39,11,"Maaku: \"Min mi yamiraama rewugol Allah, laЙ“Й“inana Mo diina kan"
  39,12,"Mi yamiraa kadi, wonugol arano e jebbiliiЙ“e Й“en"
  39,13,"Maaku : \"Min miЙ—o huli, si mi yeddii Joomi am, lepte Г‘alaande Mawnde"
  39,14,"Maaku: \"Ko Allah mi rewata, mi laЙ“Й“inan Mo diina am"
  39,15,"rewee ko yiЙ—uЙ—on onon, hara wanaa Kanko. Maaku: \"Ko woni hayruЙ“e Й“en, ko Й“en Й“e tawata Г‘alnde Darngal, Й“e hayrinii ko'e maЙ“Й“e, e Й“eynguureeji maЙ“Й“e\". Anndee ko nden woni hayrere Й“anngunde nden"
  39,16,"Hino woodirani Й“e senngo dow maЙ“Й“e, kippoodi Yiite, e kippoodi senngo ley maЙ“Й“e. Ko Й—um woni ko Allah hulЙ“inirta jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. Ko onon yo jeyaaЙ“e Am, kori hulee Lam"
  39,17,"ЖҒen woЙ—Й—itorЙ“e rewugol bewnooji Й—i, Й“e ruttii e Allah, welo-welo no woodani Й“e. Wewlinir jeyaaЙ“e Am Й“en"
  39,18,"nanooЙ“e Konngol Й“en, Й“e jokka ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e maggol. Ko Й“en woni Й“e Allah fewni Й“en, ko Й“en woni joomiraaЙ“e haqqille Й“en"
  39,19,E ko on mo konngol lepte jojji e mun... E ko an daЙ—ndata wonЙ—o ka Yiite
  39,20,"Si ko Й“en huluЙ“e Joomi mun, hino woodani Й“e kuЙ“eeje [ka Aljanna] e kuЙ“eeje mahaaЙ—e dow majje, hara canЙ—i no ila ley majje. Ko fodoore Allah ! Allah non firtataa fodoore. @Corrected"
  39,21,"E a yi'aali, wonnde Allah saaЖҙinirii ndiyam ka kammu, o naadi Й—am e nder Й“ulli ka leydi; refti O yaltinira Й—am remuru seedundu noone, refti ndu Й—ayЙ—a, yi'aa hindu soyЙ—i; refti O waЙ—a Й—um ko muncaa. Pellet, wonii e Й—um, waaju, wonannde joomiraaЙ“e haqqille Й“en"
  39,22,"E ko on mo Allah yaГұГұani Й“endre mun nden, fii lislaamu, hara himo e ndaygu immorde ka Joomi makko... Bone woodanii Й“en yooruЙ“e Й“erЙ—e mun, e jantagol Allah. ЖҒen wonii e majjere Й“anngunde"
  39,23,"Allah jippinii ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e yewtere, Deftere nanndunde [Гұaawooje], Й—immitunde. Nde guri Й“en hulooЙ“e Joomi mun riЙ“irta (nanugol nde), refti guri e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e deeЖҙira jantoore Allah nden. Ko Й—um woni peewal Allah ngal O fewnirta on Mo muuyani. Kala non mo Allah majjini, haray fewnoowo mo alaa"
  39,24,"E ko on reentariiЙ—o yeeso mun ngon, e lepte bonЙ—e Й—en Г‘alnde Darngal... TooГұuЙ“e Й“en wi'anee ontuma: \"MeeЙ—ee kon ko wonunoЙ—on faggitanaade"
  39,25,"AdinooЙ“e Й“en fenniino, lepte Й—en ardirani Й“e, ka Й“e so'aa-anndude"
  39,26,"Allah meeЙ—iniri Й“e koyeera, ka nguurndam aduna. Pellet non, ko lepte laakara Й—en non, Й“uri mawnude, si tawno hiЙ“e anndunoo"
  39,27,"GomЙ—ii Men piyanii yimЙ“e Й“en, e ndee Alqur'aanaare, kala misal, belajo'o, Й“e waajitora"
  39,28,"Alqur'aanaare (janngeteende) e haala Aarabu, nde aldaa e ooГұaare, fii no Й“e gomЙ—ira"
  39,29,"Allah waЙ—ii misal, gorko mo lurruЙ“e hawti Й—um, hiЙ“e pooЙ—ondira mo, e gorko laaЙ“anЙ—o gorko [goo]: Hara Й“en Й—iЙ—o fotay e misal? Yettoore woodanii Allah! Kono Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e anndaa"
  39,30,"Pellet, ko a maayoowo, kamЙ“e kadi ko Й“e maayooЙ“e"
  39,31,"refti onon, Г‘alnde Darngal, ko ka Joomi mon, yeddondiroyton"